      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="9951st">9951st meeting</inline>, on<docDate date="2025-06-30" refersTo="#adoptionDate">30 June 2025</docDate></docTitle>
